commentText: Indicate the items with a {@link Style}. codeText: public ConditionMessage items(Style style, Collection<?> items) {_			Assert.notNull(style, "Style must not be null")__			StringBuilder message = new StringBuilder(this.reason)__			items = style.applyTo(items)__			if ((this.condition == null || items.size() <= 1)_					&& StringUtils.hasLength(this.singular)) {_				message.append(" " + this.singular)__			}_			else if (StringUtils.hasLength(this.plural)) {_				message.append(" " + this.plural)__			}_			if (items != null && !items.isEmpty()) {_				message.append(_						" " + StringUtils.collectionToDelimitedString(items, ", "))__			}_			return this.condition.because(message.toString())__		}
